\c 6
\p
\v 1 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasikhuluma kuMozisi isithi:
\v 2 Uba umphefumulo usona\x + Nani 5.6.\x*, uphambeke isiphambeko eN\nd kosi\nd*ni ukhohlise umakhelwane wawo\x + 19.11. Efe. 4.25. Kol. 3.9.\x* mayelana lalokho okunikelwa kuwo ukuthi ukulondoloze\x + Eks. 22.7,10.\x*, loba mayelana lesibambiso sesandla, loba ngokuphangiweyo, loba umcindezele umakhelwane wawo\x + 6.4.19.13; Dute. 24.14; Mika 2.2; Mal. 3.5.\x*,
\v 3 kumbe uthola lokho okwakulahlekile\x + Dute. 22.1-3.\x*, uqambe amanga ngakho, ufunge amanga\x + Eks. 22.11.\x*, loba kukuphi kwazo zonke lezo izinto umuntu azenzayo, one ngakho,
\v 4 kuzakuthi-ke ngoba onile elecala, uzabuyisela impango ayiphangileyo, loba lokho owakuzuza ngokucindezela, loba lokho okwanikelwa kuye ukuthi akulondoloze, loba lokho okwakulahlekile akutholileyo,
\v 5 kumbe kukho konke afunge amanga ngakho; uzakubuyisa ngesiqokoqela sakho\x + 5.16. Nani 5.7.\x*, engezelele kukho ingxenye yesihlanu yakho, amnike lowo engeyakhe ngosuku lomnikelo wakhe wecala.
\v 6 Njalo uzaletha umnikelo wakhe wecala eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, inqama engelasici emhlanjini\x + 5.15,18.\x*, elesilinganiso sakho sentengo, kube ngumnikelo wecala, ayise kumpristi,
\v 7 njalo umpristi uzamenzela inhlawulo yokuthula phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*, njalo uzathethelelwa\x + 4.26.\x*, loba kukuphi kwakho konke akwenzileyo alecala ngakho.
\s Eminye imilayo ngeminikelo
\p
\v 8 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasikhuluma kuMozisi isithi:
\v 9 Laya uAroni lamadodana akhe uthi: Lo ngumlayo womnikelo wokutshiswa. Kungumnikelo wokutshiswa ngenxa yokutshisa phezu kwelathi ubusuku bonke kuze kuse, lomlilo welathi uzabhebha kulo.
\v 10 Umpristi-ke uzagqoka isembatho sakhe selembu elicolekileyo, lokabhudula wakhe wangaphansi welembu elicolekileyo\x + Eks. 28.39-42; 16.4; Hez. 44.18.\x* uzamfaka emzimbeni wakhe, athathe umlotha umlilo usuqede umnikelo wokutshiswa elathini, awubeke eceleni kwelathi\x + 1.16.\x*.
\v 11 Abesekhulula izembatho zakhe, embathe ezinye izembatho\x + 16.23. Hez. 42.14; 44.19.\x*, akhuphele umlotha ngaphandle kwenkamba endaweni ehlambulukileyo\x + 4.12.\x*.
\v 12 Lomlilo ophezu kwelathi uzabhebha kulo, ungacitshwa; njalo umpristi uzabasa inkuni phezu kwalo ukusa ngokusa, abeke kuhle umnikelo wokutshiswa phezu kwalo, atshise kulo amahwahwa eminikelo yokuthula\x + 3.3,9,14.\x*.
\v 13 Umlilo uzabhebha njalonjalo elathini, ungacitshi.
\p
\v 14 Lalo ngumlayo womnikelo wokudla\x + 2.1.\x*. Amadodana kaAroni azawunikela phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*, phambi kwelathi.
\v 15 Njalo uzacupha okwayo isandla sakhe esigcweleyo, emputshini ecolekileyo yomnikelo wokudla, lemafutheni awo, lenhlaka yonke ephezu komnikelo wokudla, akutshise elathini, uqhatshi olumnandi, isikhumbuzo sawo, eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + 2.2,9.\x*.
\v 16 Lokuseleyo kuwo uAroni lamadodana akhe bazakudla\x + 2.3. Hez. 44.29.\x*, kuzadliwa kungelamvubelo endaweni engcwele\x + 6.26; 10.12,13. Nani 18.10.\x*, lokhu bazakudla egumeni lethente lenhlangano.
\v 17 Kakuyikubhakwa ngemvubelo\x + 2.11.\x*. Kuyisabelo sabo engisinike kuminikelo yami eyenziwe ngomlilo\x + Nani 18.9.\x*; kuyingcwelengcwele\x + 6.25,29. Eks. 40.10.\x*, njengomnikelo wesono lanjengomnikelo wecala.
\v 18 Bonke abesilisa ebantwaneni bakaAroni bazakudla\x + 6.29. Nani 18.10.\x*. Kuyisimiso esilaphakade ezizukulwaneni zenu\x + 6.22; 3.17.\x*, esivela eminikelweni yeN\nd kosi\nd* eyenziwe ngomlilo; wonke okuthintayo uzakuba ngcwele\x + Eks. 29.37; 30.29; 22.3-7.\x*.
\p
\v 19 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasikhuluma kuMozisi isithi:
\v 20 Lo ngumnikelo kaAroni lamadodana akhe\x + Eks. 29.2.\x* abazawunikela eN\nd kosi\nd*ni ngosuku lokugcotshwa kwakhe; okwetshumi \w kwe-efa\w** lempuphu ecolekileyo\x + Eks. 16.36; Levi 5.11.\x* kube ngumnikelo wokudla njalonjalo, ingxenye yayo ekuseni lengxenye yayo kusihlwa.
\v 21 Uzakwenzelwa emganwini oyincence ngamafutha\x + 2.5.\x*. Uzawuletha uxutshanisiwe, unikele ngencezu ezibhakiweyo zomnikelo wokudla, zibe luqhatshi olumnandi eN\nd kosi\nd*ni.
\v 22 Lompristi wamadodana akhe, ogcotshiweyo esikhundleni sakhe, uzakwenza. Kuyisimiso saphakade eN\nd kosi\nd*ni. Uzatshiswa ngokupheleleyo\x + Eks. 29.25.\x*.
\v 23 Wonke-ke umnikelo wokudla wompristi uzatshiswa ngokupheleleyo, ungadliwa.
\p
\v 24 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasikhuluma kuMozisi isithi:
\v 25 Tshono kuAroni lakumadodana akhe uthi: Lo ngumlayo womnikelo wesono\x + 4.3.\x*. Endaweni lapho okuhlatshelwa khona umnikelo wokutshiswa umnikelo wesono uzahlatshwa khona phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*\x + 1.3,5,11; 4.24,29,33; 7.2.\x*; uyingcwelengcwele\x + 6.17,29.\x*.
\v 26 Umpristi owunikelela isono uzawudla\x + 10.17,18; Nani 18.9,19; Hez. 44.27-29.\x*; uzadlelwa endaweni engcwele\x + 6.16.\x*, egumeni lethente lenhlangano.
\v 27 Konke okuthinta inyama yawo kuzakuba ngcwele\x + 6.18.\x*; lofafaza okwegazi lawo esigqokweni, lokhu afafaze kikho wena uzakugezisa endaweni engcwele.
\v 28 Njalo imbiza yebumba okuphekelwe kuyo izaphahlazwa\x + 11.33; 15.12.\x*; kodwa uba kuphekelwe embizeni yethusi, kayiphalwe ihlanjululwe ngamanzi.
\v 29 Wonke owesilisa kubapristi uzawudla\x + 6.18.\x*. Kuyingcwelengcwele\x + 6.17,25.\x*.
\v 30 Kodwa loba yiwuphi umnikelo wesono\x + 4.7,11,12,18,21; 16.27; Heb. 13.11; 26,29; 10.18.\x* okwegazi lawo lingeniswe ethenteni lenhlangano ukwenza inhlawulo yokuthula endaweni engcwele kawuyikudliwa; uzatshiswa ngomlilo.